usage: ./webserv [config_file]
server must never block or hang request forever
use only 1 poll() for all I/O , listen included
poll() must check and read at same time
never read or write without poll()
no checking of errno after read or write
FD_SET, FD_CLR, FD_ISSET, FD_ZERO
compatible with browser of choice
version is HTTP 1.1
response status codes must be accurate
default error pages
no fork for smth else than CGI
must be able to serve fully static website
clients must be able to upload files
GET, POST, DELETE methods
listen to multiple ports
fcntl(fd, F_SETFL, O_NONBLOCK); ONLY FOR MACOS

config file:
- port
- host
first server for a host / port config will be default server
- default error pages
- limit client boddy size

